      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under blood-analogue fluid at clinically representative flow-speed combinations. Geometry and fluid properties are representative. Operating environment (temperature, pressure, EM) was not varied; validation was conducted solely under nominal laboratory conditions, which is accepted at MRL 2 without an environmental-sensitivity study."
